513
00:25:16,740 --> 00:25:18,348
And you're missing
everything, dude.

514
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:20,183
All you see
are these lab results.

515
00:25:20,185 --> 00:25:22,019
You don't even know her.
Janey,

