552
00:26:50,667 --> 00:26:51,924
No guarantees.

553
00:26:51,926 --> 00:26:53,276
They need to get her to prep.

554
00:26:53,278 --> 00:26:54,760
That's gonna take a minute.

555
00:26:54,762 --> 00:26:58,198
Meanwhile,
let's you and I have a talk.

