how long he was exposed?

566
00:27:25,035 --> 00:27:26,643
Since last night.

567
00:27:26,645 --> 00:27:28,961
Best hope is the exposure
was low-level.

568
00:27:28,963 --> 00:27:30,963
Someone vented
the room he was in,

