00:27:30,965 --> 00:27:32,540
so it's possible
he got a small dose.

570
00:27:32,542 --> 00:27:34,526
Well, here's hoping.

571
00:27:36,713 --> 00:27:39,397
Look, if this is gonna be
a lecture on addiction,

572
00:27:39,399 --> 00:27:41,232
spare me, okay?
I know it's a disease...

