00:37:02,946 --> 00:37:05,555
I'll handle the post-ops.

733
00:37:05,557 --> 00:37:07,965
And I won't say a word.

734
00:37:07,967 --> 00:37:10,226
To anyone.

735
00:37:21,406 --> 00:37:23,114
Dr. Voss.

