00:37:59,426 --> 00:38:01,093
a Sisyphean task.

753
00:38:01,095 --> 00:38:02,261
Ransomware attacks,

754
00:38:02,263 --> 00:38:04,930
gas leaks. So come on,
give me some good news.

755
00:38:04,932 --> 00:38:06,598
